Flask Application root path : /opt/Flask_APP
Flask application file : /opt/Flask_APP/app.py
Flask application wsgi file : /opt/Flask_APP/wsgi.py
Flask templates : /opt/Flask_APP/templates/
Flask application socket file : /opt/Flask_APP/app.sock

